你本身既症狀，唔洗諗住會恢復。<br />\n<br />\n叫雞係比打丁更加嚴重既邪淫，如果你忍唔到，寧願你打丁，都唔好叫雞<br />\n<br />\n戒丁最好既方法就係睇戒色文章，想成功戒Ｊ就將（戒為良藥）睇一次<br />\n學習提升覺悟，覺悟降伏心魔，唔睇（戒為良藥），基本上只係等破戒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n戒丁必睇資料：<br />\n<br />\n戒為良藥 =&gt;此為必睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.qiusuoo.com/zh-tw/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.qiusuoo.com%2Fzh-tw%2F2&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=98adfdc0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.qiusuoo.com/zh-tw/2</a><br />\n<br />\nYOUTUBE戒色圖（平時用7-8分鐘睇，睇完可以保持返警惕）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA%2Fvideos&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=e813b99e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOqQnrwWwd0zrO2tdH5-OLA/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n學佛網<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.xuefo.net/znxg_15600_2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xuefo.net%2Fznxg_15600_2.htm&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=40bb3f94\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.xuefo.net/znxg_15600_2.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n香港戒色論壇 <br />\n<a href=\"http://noj1314.258club.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnoj1314.258club.com&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=bd0813b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://noj1314.258club.com</a><br />\n<br />\n秦東魁老師=&gt; 建議手機DOWN埋&quot;喜馬拉雅ＦＭ&quot;app 去聽<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLyVAEphpUDM&d=bHO956KQIgsLkYPN5Vvl7YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=17749121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LyVAEphpUDM</a><br />\n<br />\n戒色吧=&gt; 建議去精品帖睇精品戒色文<br />\n<a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%BD%E4%C9%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftieba.baidu.com%2Ff%3Fkw%3D%25B